column5: Have a good one me brudder!

Happy Bday!!

Attaboy Art - Hope ya have a great one.
Happy 88th ....i swear you dont look a day over 87....all the best
How old does it make dudder brudder?  Must be the alcohol that keeps him looking young. Happy Birthday Art.

Geeeez, I'm glad it's your B'day and not mine. I'd hate to spend my B'day in the basement building a new lathe for turning the cork handles on your new rods.  I hope you're having a great day my friend.

Thanks all so far it has been great. I went out and ran a few calls then found a farm pond that had alot of bluegills that wanted to play tug the line. I made it back to home before the rain started so whats not to love.   Art
